<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-3539] Assertion error when forwarding to local nodes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3539</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3530&quot; title=&quot;Header class not thread safe, but mutated by multiple threads&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3530&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3530&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; introduces a regression as reported on irc:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Started a rolling upgrade from 1.0.3 to 1.0.4 now all boxes are constantly spitting out this assert: at &lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.cassandra.db.RowMutationVerbHandler.forwardToLocalNodes(RowMutationVerbHandler.java:71)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12533131">CASSANDRA-3539</key>
            <summary>Assertion error when forwarding to local nodes</summary>
